Author: manic-regressive
Text: "No seriously, like we werent expecting guests"  Cocaine and SSRIs on nightstand. Puke splattered trashcan with 200 kitkat wrappers inside. Laundry piled atop of everything. Fridge full of decaying vegetables...

Author: grumpygrumbles
Text: when you first walk in you’ll see some warm and welcoming decor including framed photos of Lily Collins, coffee, cozy spaces, and oversized fall apparel :)  come a little further into my ED crib and this is where things get a little spicy. Please ignore the empty Diet Coke Cans, smoked cigs, and Monster cans lying around, we weren’t expecting guests
